Assuming your program name is: LinkedInt
Run your program with seeds: 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Run your program with valgrind to check for memory leaks, e.g.,

LinkedInt 0     //  fixed and varied are both 0
LinkedInt 1     //  fixed 0
LinkedInt 2     //  varied 0
LinkedInt 3     //  fixed 0, varied 1
LinkedInt 4     //  fixed 1, varied 0
